lead_paragraph: Arsenal manager Arsene Wenger said on Monday he had told England boss Roy Hodgson that midfielder Jack Wilshere was progressing well from his broken calf bone and recovery was looking "good" ahead of the European Championships in France later this year.

headline.print_headline: Arsenal's Wenger Tells England Wilshere Progressing Well From Injury
headline.main: Arsenal's Wenger Tells England Wilshere Progressing Well From Injury
